  "prompt": "What do yellow roses symbolize?",
  "response": "Yellow roses primarily symbolize friendship, joy, and warmth. They are often associated with positive feelings, celebration, and new beginnings. In some contexts, yellow roses can also convey a sense of appreciation and care. Unlike other rose colors that might indicate romantic love or passion, yellow roses are more about platonic love and companionship. Additionally, they can also represent admiration and goodwill.",
